he weekend, Iran and Oman held the \"first meeting of the Hormuz Joint Committee\" in Muscat. \n\nIran's delegation led by dep foreign minister Gharibabadi, and Oman's by state foreign minister Al-Hinai. #oott", "time": "06:34", "author": "ncitayim", "author_name": "Nader Itayim | ‌‌نادر ایتیّم", "followers": 15974, "views": 4916, "likes": 16, "replies": 0, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071497372773789795", "url": "https://x.com/ORaevel/status/2071497372773789795", "text": "@CaptainRoyen Remember that the US SPR max drawing rate is itself a function of the storage level on a cavern-per-cavern basis in order to avoid collapsing casings. In other words, the more you draw from the SPR, the less you can draw from it as a flow rate.  #oil #oott https://t.co/KCogljXeDj https", "time": "07:33", "author": "ORaevel", "author_name": "Olivier Raevel", "followers": 290, "views": 1824, "likes": 15, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071513140202713286", "url": "https://x.com/MakaiMarine/status/2071513140202713286", "text": "Tanker demolition prices have bounced off of $400/ldt, aided recently by stronger regional currencies and stable steel prices. The monsoon season has started and should limit activity, but the demo market is anticipating post-war refugees.\n#oott #tankers https://t.co/iyltNsImYM", "time": "08:36", "author": "MakaiMarine", "author_name": "Makai Research", "followers": 4958, "views": 1141, "likes": 15, "replies": 2, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2071515636891562318", "url": "https://x.com/MakaiMarine/status/2071515636891562318", "text": "The state of dirty tanker vessel prices, where internal metrics are exceeding previous cycle peaks. More on this later…\n#oott #tankers $FRO $INSW $ECO $DHT https://t.co/Gu3KWbJdpd", "time": "08:46", "author": "MakaiMarine", "author_name": "Makai Research", "followers": 4958, "views": 1219, "likes": 13, "replies": 2, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2071528156482228678", "url": "https://x.com/PetroleumEcon/status/2071528156482228678", "text": "The geological #hydrogen sector is starting to attract significant venture capital, although comparisons with the development of upstream #gas look premature #OOTT #energy\nhttps://t.co/TEh5nSbOn7 https://t.co/iNKQlZMCTx", "time": "09:36", "author": "PetroleumEcon", "author_name": "Petroleum Economist", "followers": 67133, "views": 1197, "likes": 19, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Natural gas"]}}, {"id": "2071537206351868239", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2071537206351868239", "text": "That’s why oil prices aren’t rising yet (MM are currently holding a historically high number of short positions, dreaming for a quick SoH reopening )\nBut this could change dramatically within coming days\n#oott #Iran #Hormuz https://t.co/dEPTqI6VU0", "time": "10:12", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 2698, "likes": 46, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2071557470879887408", "url": "https://x.com/MktPulseIndia/status/2071557470879887408", "text": "Trump: IRAN HAS REQUESTED A MEETING. IT WILL TAKE PLACE TOMORROW IN DOHA! President DJT\n\n#OOTT #Nifty", "time": "11:32", "author": "MktPulseIndia", "author_name": "MarketPulse India", "followers": 860, "views": 630, "likes": 2, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071570844434809093", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2071570844434809093", "text": "So does Qatar need to release $6 B in frozen funds for Iran to attend Tuesday's Doha meeting?  #OOTT", "time": "12:25", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 1662, "likes": 10, "replies": 2, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071590681882116251", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2071590681882116251", "text": "With inventories impossible to track now, traders increasingly rely on curve dynamics as a proxy for forward s&amp;d expectations. This \"deceleration of backwardation\" signal (curve-momentum) turned decidely bearish and is behind the recent wave of selling.\n#oott https://t.co/pYz9eUzoFD", "time": "13:44", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 14102, "likes": 68, "replies": 7, "retweets": 17, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 26, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071606521276899329", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2071606521276899329", "text": "Spent some time with CNBC's @TheDomino on Friday talking the Iran situation - oil price is weak sentiment over decent fundamentals (inventory), strong US desire to get a deal (despite Hormuz strikes) and better floor price going forward ($75+) #EFT #OOTT\n\nhttps://t.co/Y8hDI8rqSa", "time": "14:47", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 4917, "likes": 17, "replies": 22, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071626882840203673", "url": "https://x.com/th_gambler/status/2071626882840203673", "text": "So the actual SoH recovery isn’t that big because out of 14mbpd over 6mbpd are getting exported through the red sea. So SoH recovery is what, 8mbpd? @Rory_Johnston \n\nthank you again for the Data\n\n#oott", "time": "16:08", "author": "th_gambler", "author_name": "TheRealGambler", "followers": 343, "views": 4877, "likes": 21, "replies": 2, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071642010201559263", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071642010201559263", "text": "Rig explosion in #Venezuela leaves at least 8 workers injured, sources say #oott https://t.co/bPANSn6YZt", "time": "17:08", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5691, "likes": 12, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Venezuela", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071642954632921559", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071642954632921559", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~5.5mb w/w to a multi year low of 325.7mb last week #oott      \n\nSour down ~2.7mb to 205.5mb    \nSweet down ~2.9mb to 120.9mb https://t.co/gnv7sJziwf", "time": "17:12", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 82885, "likes": 174, "replies": 22, "retweets": 37, "quotes": 8, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emoti